releases.description:
# Back from the dead :)
### Features
- Backup controls: You can now disable automatic backups on load/unload, and configure both the backup file path and the maximum number of backup files to keep;
- Custom heatmap start date: Heatmaps can now start from an arbitrary configurable date;
- Manual data entry: You can now manually insert entries for a specific date and file (helps if you want to include writing done outside of Obsidian).

### Fixes
- Auto date update: The heatmap and entries now automatically updates when the day changes, without needing a manual refresh;
- Obsidian Review: Fixes some of the warnings from unused variables and removes `eval func()`;
- Dexie conflict w/ other plugins: Database library was conflicting with other Obsidian plugins using it too.

- Adds different color settings and defaults for light and dark theme;
  - Previously the defaults where the same, breaking the visual hierarchy;
- Allows for color customization through CSS custom properties, without hardcoding style values;
